Test Scope
i.Open Swift Translator website
ii.Enter Singlish text
iii.Read Sinhala translation
iv.Validate expected output

 Setup & Execution

i.Install dependencies:-npm install
ii.Install browsers:-npx playwright install
iii.Run tests:-npx playwright test
iv.View report:-npx playwright show-report
